# sample .showmailrc
# edit and copy to $HOME/.showmailrc
# use protection 600 if this file contains a password!!!
# note that I do *not* recommend to write a password in a .showmailrc file!!!
# lines starting with hashes are comments
# non comment-lines are: server, protocol, username, password, feature
# if you do not want to specify a certain parameter, use a dash instead
mail.your-provider.de
pop3s
yourname
-
show
